0.1.3
-----

Multi-file Search

- Now capable of processing multiple files per application usage.

0.1.2
-----

Win32 Port

- Providing a pre-built distribution of the English Kabbalah suite
for Win32 based systems (7/Vista/XP/2000).

Repaired Defect in Remote File Processing

- Repaired a defect which prevented the entire contents of a remote
file from being retrieved, thus limiting search results.

0.1.1
-----

Now capable of searching remote files via libcurl.

- Added libcurl to allow for searching results on remote files, web pages, etc.
- Created stripMarkupTags() to strips markup language tags (e.g. <body>, <div>, etc.) from hypertext documents.
